lemma proj_not_same_active: assumes "enat n \<le> (n'::enat)" and "(\<not> lfinite t) \<or> n'-1 < llength t" and "\<not>(\<pi>\<^bsub>c\<^esub>(ltake n' t) = \<pi>\<^bsub>c\<^esub>(ltake n t))" shows "\<exists>k. k\<ge>n \<and> k<n' \<and> enat k < llength t \<and> \<parallel>c\<parallel>\<^bsub>lnth t k\<^esub>"
